gcc-arm-embedded

- add keys to github and gitlab

- download and run pycharm

https://www.jetbrains.com/pycharm/download/download-thanks.html?platform=linux&code=PCC

- download and install quartus prime lite edition

- download install arduino and arduino-builder https://www.arduino.cc/en/Main/Software
- Install the beta version of Teensyduino https://forum.pjrc.com/threads/38599-Teensyduino-1-31-Beta-2-Available

- download and install eagle

- make directories python_projects, ruby_projects, embedded_projects, go_projects

- add variables to .profile:

export PATH=$PATH:"arduino folder":"altera folder":"eagle folder"

- clone your repos (remember to check for submodules!)
- add udev rules for teensy, ftdi, altera
